{"word":"ἀναλόω","slug":"ἀναλόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀναλόω</el></b> [by-form of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀναλίσκω\">ἀναλίσκω</a></el>; ‘waste, expend’] ‘do away with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> completely’, of fiery action <b><i>consume</i> <a href='B:480 9:49'>Mk 9:49</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> and <b><a href='B:490 9:54'>Lk 9:54</a></b> (for the latter <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the imagistic ‘waste’ used in underworld society); <b><i>destroy</i> <a href='B:600 2:8'>2 Th 2:8</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <i>expend,</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> commercial imagery <b><a href='B:550 5:15'>Gal 5:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄναλος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνάλυσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}